        <h1 class="post-title">Why Ingredient Standardization Matters: The Foundation of Trust, Quality, and Efficacy in Nutraceutical Products</h1>
        <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="post-author">By <strong>Dr. Sreenivasa Rao Damarla</strong></span><br>
            <span class="author-title">Founder, Nutrisign Labs</span>
        </div>
